# #175: the SDK ships a COMMITTED dist/ (its `main` -> ./dist/index.js). A bare
# `dist` pattern is anchored to the context root in Docker's matcher, so it should
# not match percolator-sdk/dist — but negating explicitly makes this correct under
# either interpretation rather than relying on that detail.
!percolator-sdk/dist
